The '''2011â12 Indonesian Premier League''' season is the inaugural season of the [[Indonesian Premier League]] (IPL), a fully professional football competition that replaced the [[Indonesia Super League]] as the top tier of the [[Association football|football]] league pyramid in [[Indonesia]].

